<div class="description">
    <h3>Description</h3>

    <div class="body">
        <p>The call to load the Wurfl application class will fail if the configuration option "wurfl_lib_dir" does not contain a trailing forward slash.  To fix, on line 77 and 73 make the following change require_once ($config['wurfl_lib_dir'] . DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR . 'Application.php');</p>

